  "texts": [
    "PIV can reveal complex internal flow patterns in droplets related to Marangoni effects [27,71] and interface oscillation [61,9].",
    "However, the refraction of light at the gasliquid interface distorts the measured velocity field and necessitates complicated correction procedures [43,60] that require precise knowledge of the instantaneous 3D interface shape.Recent advances in deep learning, particularly implicit neural representations [16,59,64], offer a promising solution to this challenge.",
    "These methods train neural networks to approximate a continuous implicit representation of 3D shapes through a level-set or occupancy function.",
    "To enable reconstruction from images, the network is typically conditioned on features extracted from the input images through convolutional neural networks [72].",
    "This approach has been successfully applied to reconstruct the interface dynamics of impinging [24] and adhering droplets [25] from monocular optical experiments."
  ],
